I&#x27;ve never used emacs - Is that &#x27;select word&#x27;? I have that system-wide by putting<p><pre><code>  &quot;^w&quot; = (selectWord:);
</code></pre>
into &#x27;~/Library/KeyBindings/DefaultKeyBinding.dict&#x27;. There&#x27;s a load of information online about the customisation that can be put in this file. Here&#x27;s a comment of mine with some links in it: <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=6718604" rel="nofollow">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=6718604</a><p>Annoyingly, Xcode stopped paying attention to this file at some point around version 4, so now you have to maintain a separate version for that.
